<lb n="0652a07" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0652a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0652a09" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1158</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0652a10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0652003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】永久五年寫東山三密藏本</note>地藏菩薩儀軌</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0652a11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0652a12" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">中天竺輸婆迦羅奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0652a13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0652a1301">爾時釋迦牟尼佛。在<note n="0652004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB14305"/>＝佉【甲】</note><app n="0652004"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB14305"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">佉</rdg></app>羅提耶山。與無量諸
<lb n="0652a14" ed="T"/><note n="0652005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔地藏〕－ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652005"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">地藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩十俱胝比丘比丘尼及天龍八部
<lb n="0652a15" ed="T"/>諸鬼神俱無量百千大眾圍繞而為說法。爾
<lb n="0652a16" ed="T"/>時大眾中有一大士名曰地藏。<note n="0652006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔偏〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652006"><lem wit="【大】">偏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>袒右肩右
<lb n="0652a17" ed="T"/>膝著地。合掌恭敬白佛言。我說神呪欲利益
<lb n="0652a18" ed="T"/>一切眾生。唯願世尊欲說神呪。慈哀聽許。時
<lb n="0652a19" ed="T"/>佛告地藏菩薩言。汝等速說利益一切有情。</p>
<lb n="0652a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2001">爾時地藏菩薩騰虛空讚歎歸命世尊。<note n="0652007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">在＝有【甲】</note><app n="0652007"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">有</rdg></app>空
<lb n="0652a21" ed="T"/>中<note n="0652008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝示【甲】</note><app n="0652008"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">示</rdg></app>現無量神通。以神口說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0652a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2201" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0652009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">闇＝閻ヵ【原】，闇【甲】</note><note n="0652009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闇＝閻ヵ【原】，＝闇【甲】</note><app n="0652009"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">闇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">閻</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">闇</rdg></app>摩他<g ref="#CB03782"/>摩爾俱苾<note n="0652010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">俱苾＋（俱苾）【甲】</note><app n="0652010"><lem wit="【大】">俱苾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俱苾俱苾</rdg></app>三曼多<note n="0652011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑婆賀＝沙呵【甲】＊</note><app n="0652011"><lem wit="【大】">娑婆
<lb n="0652a23" ed="T"/>賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙呵</rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2302" rend="inline">次<note n="0652012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝脫ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652012"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">脫</rdg></app>心呪。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2306" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵炎曼他<note n="0652013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">啫＝嗜【甲】</note><app n="0652013"><lem wit="【大】">啫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嗜</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0652011"><lem wit="【大】">娑婆賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙呵</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2401"><note n="0652014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＋（說）【甲】</note><app n="0652014"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">次說</rdg></app>心中心呪。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2406" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵<note n="0652015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">礘＝濕ヵ【原】，砥ヵ【原】，矷【甲】</note><note n="0652015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">礘＝濕ヵ【原】，＝砥ヵ【原】，＝矷【甲】</note><app n="0652015"><lem wit="【大】">礘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">砥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">矷</rdg></app>呬<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0652a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2501">纔說此呪。十地等大菩薩。失本心迷惑。天龍
<lb n="0652a26" ed="T"/>八部藥叉鬼神驚走倒地。日月星宿失光隱
<lb n="0652a27" ed="T"/><note n="0652016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蔽＝弊【甲】</note><app n="0652016"><lem wit="【大】">蔽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">弊</rdg></app><note n="0652017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">空雨＝雨空【甲】</note><app n="0652017"><lem wit="【大】">空。雨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">雨空</rdg></app>寶華繽紛。窮劫說呪力不可說
<lb n="0652a28" ed="T"/>盡。</p>
<lb n="0652a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652a2901">次說畫像法。作聲聞形像。著袈裟端覆左肩。
<pb n="0652b" xml:id="T20.1158.0652b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0652b01" ed="T"/>左手持盈華形。右手施無畏令坐蓮華。復<note n="0652018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（作）＋居【甲】</note><app n="0652018"><lem wit="【大】">居</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">作居</rdg></app>
<lb n="0652b02" ed="T"/>座大士像頂著天冠著袈裟。左手持蓮華<note n="0652019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝葉ヵ【原】，莖ヵ【原】，坐【甲】</note><note n="0652019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝葉ヵ【原】，＝莖ヵ【原】，＝坐【甲】</note><app n="0652019"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">葉</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">莖</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">坐</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0652b03" ed="T"/>右手如先令安坐九品蓮臺<note place="inline">傳云九品者九重<note n="0652020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也亦…也〕八字－【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0652020"><lem wit="【大】">也亦云八葉中臺也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>。</p>
<lb n="0652b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0401">次說<note n="0652021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝身【甲】</note><app n="0652021"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">身</rdg></app>呪<note n="0652022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652022"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>二羽三補吒。戒方內掌來
<lb n="0652b05" ed="T"/>去。<note n="0652023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪曰〕－ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652023"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">呪曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0504" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵炎摩智利<app type="star" corresp="#0652011"><lem wit="【大】">娑婆賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙呵</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0601">次說普供<note n="0652024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔養〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652024"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。禪智立來去。</p>
<lb n="0652b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0701" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0652025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喃＝布【甲】</note><app n="0652025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">布</rdg></app>惹摩尼<note n="0652026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑嚩賀＝沙<g ref="#CB01239"/>【甲】</note><app n="0652026"><lem wit="【大】">娑嚩賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙<g ref="#CB01239"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0801">次總<note n="0652027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔說總〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652027"><lem wit="【大】">說總</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。進力<note n="0652028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔立〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652028"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>來去。呪
<lb n="0652b09" ed="T"/>曰。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0652b0902" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵<g ref="#CB03777"/>只儞耶<note n="0652029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑嚩二合賀＝沙<g ref="#CB01239"/>【甲】</note><app n="0652029"><lem wit="【大】">娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙<g ref="#CB01239"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b1001">次請<note n="0652030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔讚〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652030"><lem wit="【大】">讚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。進力來去次<note n="0652031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撥＝蕟【甲】</note><app n="0652031"><lem wit="【大】">撥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蕟</rdg></app>遣
<lb n="0652b11" ed="T"/>以觀手禪進彈。</p>
<lb n="0652b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0652b1201">復說成就法。若念得大<note n="0652032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">福＝富【甲】</note><app n="0652032"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">富</rdg></app>德。持阿迦木護摩
<lb n="0652b13" ed="T"/><note n="0652033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（滿）＋七【甲】</note><app n="0652033"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">滿七</rdg></app>萬遍。若念得五穀成就。以稻實華護摩。
<lb n="0652b14" ed="T"/>若念他人福德。取得其家<note n="0652034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">竈土＝竈五土取【甲】</note><app n="0652034"><lem wit="【大】">竈土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竈五土取</rdg></app>護摩。若念得
<lb n="0652b15" ed="T"/>高位<note n="0652035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝高【甲】</note><app n="0652035"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">高</rdg></app>德。以比哩華護摩。若念生生世世怨
<lb n="0652b16" ed="T"/>敵伏。以苦<note n="0652036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔練〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652036"><lem wit="【大】">練</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>木護摩。若念惡靈邪<note n="0652037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">家＝氣【甲】</note><app n="0652037"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">氣</rdg></app>伏。以
<lb n="0652b17" ed="T"/>毒味護摩。若念顛狂<note n="0652038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">痾＝癎【甲】</note><app n="0652038"><lem wit="【大】">痾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">癎</rdg></app><note n="0652039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＋（及痔病）【甲】</note><app n="0652039"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">病及痔病</rdg></app>除愈。<note n="0652040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蓮＝連【甲】</note><app n="0652040"><lem wit="【大】">蓮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">連</rdg></app><note n="0652041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">實＝寶ィ【原】</note><app n="0652041"><lem wit="【大】">實</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">寶</rdg></app>草
<lb n="0652b18" ed="T"/>護摩。三萬遍。若念滅罪生善<note n="0652042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝捨ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652042"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">捨</rdg></app>身後生極
<lb n="0652b19" ed="T"/>樂<note n="0652043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＋（迦）【甲】</note><app n="0652043"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以迦</rdg></app>草護摩三萬遍。若念惡人呪咀還著本
<lb n="0652b20" ed="T"/>人。以苦草投火中護摩三萬遍。若念得無量
<lb n="0652b21" ed="T"/>榮果俸祿。<note n="0652044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白華鳥＝白在以鳥【甲】</note><app n="0652044"><lem wit="【大】">白華鳥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">白在以鳥</rdg></app>草護摩三萬遍。若念三昧
<lb n="0652b22" ed="T"/>辨<note n="0652045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">財＝才【甲】</note><app n="0652045"><lem wit="【大】">財</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">才</rdg></app><note n="0652046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">德＝得【甲】</note><app n="0652046"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">得</rdg></app>者。以<note n="0652047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔骨〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652047"><lem wit="【大】">骨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婁草護摩三萬遍。若念化
<lb n="0652b23" ed="T"/>度一切眾生令離苦得樂。以白芥子護摩三
<lb n="0652b24" ed="T"/>萬遍。若念化度無佛世界眾生。以尸迦草護
<lb n="0652b25" ed="T"/>摩三<note n="0652048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七〕－ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652048"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>萬遍。若念枯田畠五穀生者。加持
<lb n="0652b26" ed="T"/>古蔓菁。加持<note n="0652049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散＋（其所）【甲】</note><app n="0652049"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">散其所</rdg></app>。若愁萬病者。牛膝草護摩
<lb n="0652b27" ed="T"/>三萬遍。若愁三陰四熱種種病。以降乾<note n="0652050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">各＝天ヵ【原】</note><app n="0652050"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">天</rdg></app>門
<lb n="0652b28" ed="T"/>草護摩。若夫妻不和者。比<note n="0652051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">罪＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0652051"><lem wit="【大】">罪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app>草護摩三萬
<lb n="0652b29" ed="T"/>遍和合。若惡友善友相違者。藤葉草護摩三
<pb n="0652c" xml:id="T20.1158.0652c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0652c01" ed="T"/>萬遍。若白月八日十四日。十五日<note n="0652052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652052"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>上法修
<lb n="0652c02" ed="T"/>必得成就。</p>
